  "title": "Contracts Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Contracts Manager</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To preform Contract agreement review.</p>\n<p>To perform Contract and commercial risk assessment.</p>\n<p>To develop and implement construction commercial proposal.</p>\n<p>To resolve Construction dispute settlement.</p>\n<p>To oversee and ensure that budgets are kept and that projects operations are not hampered due to budget allocations.</p>\n<p>To meet, build and maintain relationships with Clients, Contractors, Suppliers and Sub-contractors.</p>\n<p>To prepare and submit quarterly reports.</p>\n<p>Involve in project tender</p>\n<p>Minimum 5/6 years experience.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
